00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.527
Hi! today we'll make this nice little box

00:00:01.527 --> 00:00:04.157
to keep the cards and envelopes we make last video

00:00:04.157 --> 00:00:11.157
stay with me and subscribe to my channel

00:00:14.826 --> 00:00:16.257
comienza recordando

00:00:16.257 --> 00:00:17.916
start cutting a cardstock rectangle

00:00:17.916 --> 00:00:21.347
22 by 13 cm

00:00:21.347 --> 00:00:22.287
let's score it

00:00:22.287 --> 00:00:25.806
along

00:00:25.806 --> 00:00:27.176
at 6, 7,

00:00:27.176 --> 00:00:30.277
16 and 17 cm

00:00:30.277 --> 00:00:33.717
and widthwise let's score at

00:00:33.717 --> 00:00:36.717
at 1, 2, 11

00:00:36.717 --> 00:00:43.717
and 12 cm

00:01:05.787 --> 00:01:12.787
fold your cardstock on the scores

00:01:19.237 --> 00:01:26.237
now cut the external rectangles from the 4 corners

00:01:28.557 --> 00:01:33.797
your box must be like this

00:01:33.797 --> 00:01:40.797
cut now the little flaps... remove the upper ones and saving the lowers

00:01:41.787 --> 00:01:45.987
to make the box backing

00:01:45.987 --> 00:01:52.987
choose a washi tape to decorate the box sides

00:02:03.167 --> 00:02:10.167
well cover the sides and cut the leftover

00:02:35.806 --> 00:02:42.806
your box must be like this

00:02:43.146 --> 00:02:48.016
now cover the lower flap with another washi tape color

00:02:48.016 --> 00:02:55.016
and cut the leftover

00:03:07.746 --> 00:03:10.266
use a third washi tape color and cover the upper flap

00:03:10.266 --> 00:03:17.266
te cobran las solapas superior

00:03:58.786 --> 00:04:02.216
put now a self-adhesive magnet

00:04:02.216 --> 00:04:04.276
on the lower flap

00:04:04.276 --> 00:04:11.276
us on the upper one... then glue the box by the small flaps

00:04:37.536 --> 00:04:44.536
now

00:04:51.907 --> 00:04:54.136
glue the lower flap on top of the sides...
Decorate with ribbon

00:04:54.136 --> 00:05:01.136
gluing a long strip along the box and finishing with a loop

00:05:30.087 --> 00:05:32.497
finally glue the loop

00:05:32.497 --> 00:05:34.927
and the box will be ready

00:05:34.927 --> 00:05:38.096
this box is a kit for cards and envelopes

